{"id": 2565, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你认为什么是真正意义上的\"无聊\"？", "description": "很多时候无聊并不意味着没事做，而往往是为了避免无聊做了一些更无聊的事。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA Images )", "record_count": 5199, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181019154650ch97DOJv03PUlHuK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 305152, "content": "怎么也找不到感兴趣的事情 所以无所事事 做别的事又感到很无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475316}, {"id": 305408, "content": "成功之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204585}, {"id": 305664, "content": "打开好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471454}, {"id": 305153, "content": "想要说话的人，不鸟你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441639}, {"id": 305409, "content": "就想荒废时间，不想做要思考的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440096}, {"id": 305154, "content": "我在这里留评论，说明我真的无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475320}, {"id": 305410, "content": "明明没有任何事情需要做，却被强行加班，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356853}, {"id": 305156, "content": "两个人同时拿出手机的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252093}, {"id": 305157, "content": "国庆节图书馆关门又不想出去玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156636}, {"id": 305159, "content": "我居然在很认真的思考这个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288801}, {"id": 305415, "content": "时不时的点亮手机屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476182}, {"id": 305671, "content": "手机下游戏，登入超过一分钟立马删", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477329}, {"id": 305160, "content": "贤者时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118633}, {"id": 305161, "content": "做着无聊的事最无聊 还很痛苦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475340}, {"id": 305674, "content": "躺在床上，望着天花板，想着什么，却又动不起来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477177}, {"id": 305163, "content": "喜欢在手机上下载一堆电影美剧，但基本没怎么看过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475342}, {"id": 305675, "content": "是加入聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477357}, {"id": 307979, "content": "真正无聊的人察觉不到自己无聊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488432}, {"id": 305164, "content": "明明有一堆事情要干却拖着不干，而后拿着手机无所事事的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473721}, {"id": 305420, "content": "娱乐新闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453801}, {"id": 305165, "content": "就像现在\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1452569}, {"id": 305166, "content": "不断地刷新消息页面，希望有人发信息给自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458877}, {"id": 305422, "content": "不停地刷手机，看游戏新闻，下载新游戏又卸载。打开社交app不停地匹配又退出，不停地找人聊天又不知道最后留下了什么。晚上不想睡觉但明明手机也没什么好玩的就是要玩。用短期的快乐满足自己，结束后又无聊。为了缓解这一无聊，又变得更加无聊。想想并不是无聊，而是逃避，只有进取和创新才会有聊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337877}, {"id": 305167, "content": "刷抖音", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011810}, {"id": 305679, "content": "假日逛街想好了行程，然而到头来就独自吃了个饭回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446964}, {"id": 305680, "content": "打开网页发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477039}, {"id": 306704, "content": "心里突然咯噔了一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481818}, {"id": 305169, "content": "上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117088}, {"id": 305170, "content": "对未来没方向，又不甘寂寞，又没有行动，也不会消磨时光，更不会享受生活。那就很无聊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475371}, {"id": 305171, "content": "想找的人却不在", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474033}, {"id": 305172, "content": "上着大学，待在宿舍一天，一直刷uc刷到更新重复。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475372}, {"id": 305428, "content": "千篇一律的会议\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919453}, {"id": 305173, "content": "任何东西的重复都是无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400904}, {"id": 305685, "content": "一个人在家的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453061}, {"id": 305174, "content": "没有生活目标，饿不死也吃不饱，想要努力，找不到目标，不知道该干什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466671}, {"id": 305175, "content": "看到大家居然都跟我一样无聊突然感觉不无聊了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1169253}, {"id": 305176, "content": "没有奔头", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475380}, {"id": 305432, "content": "我老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446337}, {"id": 305177, "content": "重复很多次", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359402}, {"id": 305179, "content": "日复一日机械式的做着同样的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475377}, {"id": 305435, "content": "手机突然没电之后...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145248}, {"id": 305180, "content": "你们现在屏幕看到的就是无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469020}, {"id": 305181, "content": "无穷无尽的开会（手机玩没电了，觉也睡够了），看着领导的脸放空", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718997}, {"id": 305183, "content": "心中空虚，无以充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801641}, {"id": 305184, "content": "走弯路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475385}, {"id": 305185, "content": "不停的刷新好奇心研究所的主页、朋友圈等等等社交软件，然鹅没刷出什么新的东西。于是就去找一个跟你一样无聊的人开始磨牙式聊天， 训练抬杠技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475384}, {"id": 305186, "content": "在手机上各种APP间切来切去，但真没什么好看的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890948}, {"id": 305442, "content": "失去梦想的那一刻，不管是怎样的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1472144}, {"id": 305698, "content": "坐着，无所事事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477427}, {"id": 305954, "content": "左翻朋友圈，又翻朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441740}]}